    section.slide
      h2 Chrome 77
      img(src='../../shared/resources/images/chrome.png', class='corner-image', width='200px', alt='Chrome')
      p Released September 17th — 
        a(href='https://developers.google.com/web/updates/2019/09/nic77') Release Notes
        |  (
        a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8aVB3IfOR4') video
        | )
      h3.star Largest Contentful Paint
      ul
        li Measure render time of the 
          a(href='https://web.dev/largest-contentful-paint/') largest content element
        li Best real-world way to measure user-facing performance
        li Uses the 
          a(href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceEntry')
            span.code PerformanceEntry
          |  event of type 
          span.code largest-contentful-paint

    section.slide
      h2 Chrome 77
      img(src='../../shared/resources/images/chrome.png', class='corner-image', width='200px', alt='Chrome')
      h3.star Easier Custom Form Components
      ul 
        li New 
          span.code formdata
          |  event for appending custom data on submit
        pre
          code
            | const form = document.querySelector('form');
            | form.addEventListener('formdata', ({formData}) => {
            |   formData.append('my-input', myInputValue);
            | });
        p
          a(href='https://web.dev/more-capable-form-controls/#event-based-api') Learn more

    section.slide
      h2 Chrome 77
      img(src='../../shared/resources/images/chrome.png', class='corner-image', width='200px', alt='Chrome')
      h3.star Easier Custom Form Components
      ul 
        li New 
          span.code formAssociated
          |  property links custom components to a form
        li You provide the field API like 
          span.code .name
          | , 
          span.code .value
          | , etc.
        pre
          code
            | class MyInput extends HTMLElement {
            |   static formAssociated = true;
            |   get value() { return this.value_; }
            |   ...
            | }
        p
          a(href='https://web.dev/more-capable-form-controls/#defining-a-form-associated-custom-element') Learn more

    section.slide
      h2 Chrome 77
      img(src='../../shared/resources/images/chrome.png', class='corner-image', width='200px', alt='Chrome')
      h3.star Copy Styles
