      p Released September 3rd — 
        a(href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/69') Release Notes
      h3.star Massive Privacy Release
      ul
        li Enhanced Tracking Protection (ETP)  
          a(href='https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2019/09/03/todays-firefox-blocks-third-party-tracking-cookies-and-cryptomining-by-default/') enabled by default
        li Blocks all third-party tracking cookies and cryptominers
        li 
          a(href='https://blog.mozilla.org/firefox/how-to-block-fingerprinting-with-firefox/') Fingerprinting scripts
          |  can be blocked by enabling "Strict Mode"
        li New option to 
          a(href='https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/block-autoplay') block all autoplay media
          |  by default
        li Flash is also now 
          a(href='https://www.zdnet.com/article/mozilla-firefox-69-will-disable-adobe-flash-plugin-by-default/') disabled by default

